Her makeover, which features a coastal-inspired pool house, an Adirondack lawn bar, and a poolside lounge, has us dreaming of relaxing by the pool and dining alfresco. Visit the link in our profile to read more about this coastal retreat. 📷 @ryangarvin #serenaandlily
